Package com.swoval.files.apple

Class Flags.Event

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.swoval.files.apple.Flags.Event
  • Enclosing class:
    Flags
    public static class Flags.Event
extends java.lang.Object
    Wrapper around the file system event flags. The main purpose of this class is to avoid having to directly manipulate the underlying integer containing the flag values.
